==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Copartner
<hw>Co*part"ner</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is jointly
concerned with one or more persons in business, etc.; a partner; an
associate; a partaker; a sharer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>the associates and <qex>copartners</qex> of our loss.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Copartnership</ent>⟦br⟧
